Java program to add two numbers using method

[Java program to add two numbers using method](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/java-program-to-add-two-numbers-using-method/)

Hereâ€™s the java program to add two numbers using function.

import java.util.Scanner;
public class AddTwoNumbers
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      int num1, num2, sum;
      Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
      System.out.println("First number : ");
      num1 = sc.nextInt();
      System.out.println("Second number : ");
      num2 = sc.nextInt();
      sum = addTwo(num1, num2);
      System.out.println("Sum : " + sum);
      sc.close();
   }
   public static int addTwo(int a, int b)
   {
      int sum = a + b;
      return sum;
   }
}

